title: Gross domestic product ( GDP ) growth rate in Oman 2024
yAxis: GDP growth compared to previous year
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing GDP growth compared to previous year, containing a total of 11 data points.
Overall GDP growth compared to previous year has increased over the Year.
GDP growth compared to previous year is roughly constant from 2014 to 2019, gradually increasing from 2019 to 2020, and lastly roughly constant from 2020 to 2024.
Maximum GDP growth compared to previous year, about 4.9 was reported at Year 2016
Minimum GDP growth compared to previous year about 0.04 was reached at Year 2019
